{"tid":2209362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）舊年平安夜係尖沙咀過既手足入一入黎 （2）","createTime":"2020-09-19T15:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T18:43:21.000Z","uid":221995,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"add2c91b05354a7b92acc5d3ac9178d8ff273092","tid":2209362,"uid":221995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"上一個post 好多謝咁多手足幫手推推爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2204649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2204649</a><br />\n全靠咁多位手足幫忙 我地都搵到好多事發既片段 好多手足都提供左好多資料同片段<br />\n好多謝聯絡左我地提供資料同幫手轉推share既手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地只能無言感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但暫時未搵到當日既在場人士 希望手足可以幫手繼續推同share去唔同既fb 或者 tg  <br />\n同時希望當日在場記者拍攝都可以幫幫手提供資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為當日好多傳媒live直播都有拍攝到部分過程<br />\n我地都有send過email去唔同傳媒網媒 希望佢地都可以提供協助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提供到更多當時事發相片 希望當日在場人士可以認到自己<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DWqUjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DWqUjH.png&h=4bd05dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/amYdiME.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FamYdiME.png&h=52a3eafd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mviwPTz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmviwPTz.png&h=c0cdea6e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FopDuTT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFopDuTT.png&h=14b247e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n⚠️需要被制服前影片及目擊者<br />\n⚠️麻煩大家share去唔同平台<br />\n<br />\n編號：#EVI087<br />\n案發日期：2019年12月24日<br />\n案發時間：晚上8點半至9點<br />\n案發地點：#尖沙咀 中間道及彌敦道交界<br />\n需要影片：需要任何於上述時間拍攝到的影片 (最好有影片擁有者)<br />\n<br />\n如果你當時在場請聯絡: <br />\nTelegram: @youarenotalonehk_evibot<br />\nEmail: poposikshitlah@protonmail.ch<br />\n<br />\n另外希望手足保持關注12位被送中手足並參與聯署<br />\n【全球聯署！要求中國政府送返12名被捕港人 &mdash;&mdash; Immediate Return of the 12 HK Detainees from Mainland China!】<br />\nGlobal Petition: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fsave12youthspetitions&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=75b5d77b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/save12youthspetitions</a>"},{"pid":"89d235884e7dc007551c2c1091b3b3a59f15771b","tid":2209362,"uid":12629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"幫手堆"},{"pid":"71e88e85db682c12daf56a434f5aead98987b9cc","tid":2209362,"uid":221995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:04:54.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ac8d31a7bdf7dc77478f4480fdddff573d0ab6","tid":2209362,"uid":146434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:14:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e8b5e27b511be54779c3fae7043a0928631beaa5","tid":2209362,"uid":277572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b5f61aeca6c558963444cf887132a77cf6ac0b","tid":2209362,"uid":146601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.